---

<section id="about" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-gold font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-sm mb-3">July 3, 2026</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-navy mb-6">The Countdown Is On</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-red mx-auto"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Two column layout -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Text -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          Fifty years ago, Washington, D.C. stood at the center of one of the most memorable
          celebrations in American history: the Bicentennial of the United States. It was a moment
          of grandeur, pride, and patriotism that left an indelible mark on a generation.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          Now, as America prepares to celebrate 250 years of freedom, courage, and unity,
          history comes alive once again.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          On July 3rd, 2026, proud Americans from across the nation and around the world will
          gather in Washington, D.C. for the most historic patriotic weekend of our generation.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg font-medium text-navy">
          Be there when history begins.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="relative">
        <img
          src="/countdown250/images/event-photos/aab-2013-color-guard-1.jpg"
          alt="Military color guard at a previous All-American Ball"
          class="rounded-lg shadow-xl w-full object-cover aspect-[4/3]"
        />
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-32 h-32 bg-navy/10 rounded-lg -z-10"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Why July 3rd -->
    <div class="mt-20 bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12">
      <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-6 text-center">Why July 3rd Matters</h3>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4 text-center">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate">
          July 4, 2026 marks the 250th anniversary of the United States of America.
          A milestone that will only occur once in our lifetimes.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate">
          Across the country, communities will celebrate this extraordinary moment. But in
          Washington, D.C., the celebration begins the night before, when thousands gather to
          launch the historic anniversary weekend.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate font-medium">
          The Countdown 250 Ball brings together leaders, heroes, entertainers, and
          proud Americans for a night of patriotism, inspiration, and celebration.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
